      #caption2.one-col
        %p
          The spreadsheet was an infinite canvas of tile
          %span.kern s.
          There were no limitations on the number of images, and how many tiles each images takes u
          %span.kern p.
        %p This was causing the scrolling and other animation to slow way down. The extreme case is a single image per tile (row and column).
