      #caption4.one-col
        %p We looked to the world of mobile gaming, where the rendering wasn't done with Apple's UIKit, but the lower-level OpenGL.
        %p
          I made a prototype of the home view in OpenGL, and the performance looked promisin
          %span.kern g.
        %p
          We decided to convert the spreadsheet canvas to OpenGL and stress tested i
          %span.kern t.
          We were now getting a consistent 60fp
          %span.kern s.
          It felt so much more responsive in the hands of the use
          %span.kern r.
        %p
          While the new user experience was superio
          %span.kern r,
